    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43556</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_027_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>やっぱり……あの精霊は
エトを狙ったんですか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I knew it...that Spirit is fixated on Eto. But, why would he?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43684</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_027_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>わからない。彼女は小さかったから、
人よりも狙いやすかっただけかもしれないし</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I'm not sure. This little girl is the first person I ever heard to be targeted by a Spirit.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43772</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_027_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>まさか……！　食べるため、とか……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Could it be...!? Does he want to eat her!?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43876</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_027_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>何言ってんだよ、&lt;Mel&gt;！
違う！　……違う、よな！？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What are you saying, &lt;Dio&gt;!? That's impossible...It IS impossible, right?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44000</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_027_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>精霊はマナを生命力にしている。
具体的に何か食べて生きているわけじゃない</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Summon Spirits live through Mana. In short, they don't need to eat anything at all.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44064</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_027_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>よかった……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What a relief...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44128</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_027_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>クルール～</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Kururu~!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44268</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_027_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>だが、もしかしたら彼女自身に理由があった場合、
精霊は彼女を排除しようとするかもしれない</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Anyhow, this is a pretty unique case. We have no idea what the real reason behind this is.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44368</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_027_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あんま悠長にもしてらんないってことだね、
行くぜ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We mustn't take this lightly. Let's move forward!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44424</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_027_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ああ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Right.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44496</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_027_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>エト、無事でいて……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Eto, please be ok...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
